387     * @throws \Exception

394    /**
395     * Does a file support UnserializePhpPresentation ?
396     *
397     * @throws \Exception
398     */
399    public function fileSupportsUnserializePhpPresentation(string $pFilename = ''): bool
400    {
401        // Check if file exists
402        if (!file_exists($pFilename)) {
403            throw new \Exception('Could not open ' . $pFilename . ' for reading! File does not exist.');
404        }
405
406        try {
407            // Use ParseXL for the hard work.
408            $ole = new OLERead();
409            // get excel data
410            $ole->read($pFilename);
411
412            return true;
413        } catch (\Exception $e) {
414            return false;
415        }
416    }

418    /**
419     * Loads PhpPresentation Serialized file.
420     *
421     * @throws \Exception
422     */
423    public function load(string $pFilename): PhpPresentation
424    {
425        // Unserialize... First make sure the file supports it!
426        if (!$this->fileSupportsUnserializePhpPresentation($pFilename)) {
427            throw new \Exception("Invalid file format for PhpOffice\PhpPresentation\Reader\PowerPoint97: " . $pFilename . '.');
428        }
429
430        return $this->loadFile($pFilename);
431    }

433    /**
434     * Load PhpPresentation Serialized file.
435     *
436     * @throws \Exception
437     */
438    private function loadFile(string $pFilename): PhpPresentation
439    {
440        $this->oPhpPresentation = new PhpPresentation();
441        $this->oPhpPresentation->removeSlideByIndex();
442
443        // Read OLE Blocks
444        $this->loadOLE($pFilename);
445        // Read pictures in the Pictures Stream
446        $this->loadPicturesStream();
447        // Read information in the Current User Stream
448        $this->loadCurrentUserStream();
449        // Read information in the PowerPoint Document Stream
450        $this->loadPowerpointDocumentStream();
451
452        return $this->oPhpPresentation;
453    }
454
455    /**
456     * Read OLE Part.
457     *
458     * @throws \Exception
459     */
460    private function loadOLE(string $pFilename): void
461    {
462        // OLE reader
463        $oOLE = new OLERead();
464        $oOLE->read($pFilename);
465
466        // PowerPoint Document Stream
467        $this->streamPowerpointDocument = $oOLE->getStream($oOLE->powerpointDocument);
468
469        // Current User Stream
470        $this->streamCurrentUser = $oOLE->getStream($oOLE->currentUser);
471
472        // Get summary information data
473        $this->streamSummaryInformation = $oOLE->getStream($oOLE->summaryInformation);
474
475        // Get additional document summary information data
476        $this->streamDocumentSummaryInformation = $oOLE->getStream($oOLE->docSummaryInfos);
477
478        // Get pictures data
479        $this->streamPictures = $oOLE->getStream($oOLE->pictures);
480    }
481
482    /**
483     * Stream Pictures.
484     *
485     * @see http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd920746(v=office.12).aspx
486     */
487    private function loadPicturesStream(): void
488    {
489        $stream = $this->streamPictures;
490
491        $pos = 0;
492        do {
493            $arrayRH = $this->loadRecordHeader($stream, $pos);
494            $pos += 8;
495            $readSuccess = false;
496            if (0x00 == $arrayRH['recVer'] && (0xF007 == $arrayRH['recType'] || ($arrayRH['recType'] >= 0xF018 && $arrayRH['recType'] <= 0xF117))) {
497                //@link : http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd950560(v=office.12).aspx
498                if (0xF007 == $arrayRH['recType']) {
499                    // OfficeArtFBSE
500                    throw new \Exception('Feature not implemented (l.' . __LINE__ . ')');
501                }
502                if ($arrayRH['recType'] >= 0xF018 && $arrayRH['recType'] <= 0xF117) {
503                    $arrayRecord = $this->readRecordOfficeArtBlip($stream, $pos - 8);
504                    if ($arrayRecord['length'] > 0) {
505                        $pos += $arrayRecord['length'];
506                        $this->arrayPictures[] = $arrayRecord['picture'];
507                    }
508                }
509                $readSuccess = true;
510            }
511        } while (true === $readSuccess);
512    }
513
514    /**
515     * Stream Current User.
516     *
517     * @see http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd908567(v=office.12).aspx
518     */
519    private function loadCurrentUserStream(): void
520    {
521        $pos = 0;
522
523        /**
524         * CurrentUserAtom : http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd948895(v=office.12).aspx.
525         */
526        // RecordHeader : http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd926377(v=office.12).aspx
527        $rHeader = $this->loadRecordHeader($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
528        $pos += 8;
529        if (0x0 != $rHeader['recVer'] || 0x000 != $rHeader['recInstance'] || self::RT_CURRENTUSERATOM != $rHeader['recType']) {
530            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > RecordHeader).');
531        }
532
533        // Size
534        $size = self::getInt4d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
535        $pos += 4;
536        if (0x00000014 != $size) {
537            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > Size).');
538        }
539
540        // headerToken
541        $headerToken = self::getInt4d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
542        $pos += 4;
543        if (0xF3D1C4DF == $headerToken && 0xE391C05F != $headerToken) {
544            throw new \Exception('Feature not implemented (l.' . __LINE__ . ') : Encrypted file');
545        }
546
547        // offsetToCurrentEdit
548        $this->offsetToCurrentEdit = self::getInt4d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
549        $pos += 4;
550
551        // lenUserName
552        $lenUserName = self::getInt2d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
553        $pos += 2;
554        if ($lenUserName > 255) {
555            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > lenUserName).');
556        }
557
558        // docFileVersion
559        $docFileVersion = self::getInt2d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
560        $pos += 2;
561        if (0x03F4 != $docFileVersion) {
562            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > docFileVersion).');
563        }
564
565        // majorVersion
566        $majorVersion = self::getInt1d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
567        ++$pos;
568        if (0x03 != $majorVersion) {
569            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > majorVersion).');
570        }
571
572        // minorVersion
573        $minorVersion = self::getInt1d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
574        ++$pos;
575        if (0x00 != $minorVersion) {
576            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > minorVersion).');
577        }
578
579        // unused
580        $pos += 2;
581
582        // ansiUserName
583        // $ansiUserName = '';
584        do {
585            $char = self::getInt1d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
586            if (($char >= 0x00 && $char <= 0x1F) || ($char >= 0x7F && $char <= 0x9F)) {
587                $char = false;
588            } else {
589                // $ansiUserName .= chr($char);
590                ++$pos;
591            }
592        } while (false !== $char);
593
594        // relVersion
595        $relVersion = self::getInt4d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
596        $pos += 4;
597        if (0x00000008 != $relVersion && 0x00000009 != $relVersion) {
598            throw new \Exception('File PowerPoint 97 in error (Location : CurrentUserAtom > relVersion).');
599        }
600
601        // unicodeUserName
602        // $unicodeUserName = '';
603        for ($inc = 0; $inc < $lenUserName; ++$inc) {
604            $char = self::getInt2d($this->streamCurrentUser, $pos);
605            if (($char >= 0x00 && $char <= 0x1F) || ($char >= 0x7F && $char <= 0x9F)) {
606                break;
607            }
608            // $unicodeUserName .= chr($char);
609            $pos += 2;
610        }
611    }
612
613    /**
614     * Stream Powerpoint Document.
615     *
616     * @see http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd921564(v=office.12).aspx
617     */
618    private function loadPowerpointDocumentStream(): void
619    {
620        $this->readRecordUserEditAtom($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $this->offsetToCurrentEdit);
621
622        $this->readRecordPersistDirectoryAtom($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $this->offsetPersistDirectory);
623
624        foreach ($this->rgPersistDirEntry as $offsetDir) {
625            $pos = $offsetDir;
626
627            $rHeader = $this->loadRecordHeader($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $pos);
628            $pos += 8;
629            $this->inMainType = $rHeader['recType'];
630            $this->currentNote = null;
631            switch ($rHeader['recType']) {
632                case self::RT_DOCUMENT:
633                    $this->readRecordDocumentContainer($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $pos);
634                    break;
635                case self::RT_NOTES:
636                    $this->readRecordNotesContainer($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $pos);
637                    break;
638                case self::RT_SLIDE:
639                    $this->readRecordSlideContainer($this->streamPowerpointDocument, $pos);
640                    break;
641                default:
642                    // throw new \Exception('Feature not implemented : l.'.__LINE__.'('.dechex($rh['recType']).')');
643                    break;
644            }
645        }
646    }
647
648    /**
649     * Read a record header.
650     *
651     * @return array<string, int>
652     */
653    private function loadRecordHeader(string $stream, int $pos): array
654    {
655        $rec = self::getInt2d($stream, $pos);
656        $recType = self::getInt2d($stream, $pos + 2);
657        $recLen = self::getInt4d($stream, $pos + 4);
658
659        return [
660            'recVer' => ($rec >> 0) & bindec('1111'),

668     * Read 8-bit unsigned integer.
669     */
670    public static function getInt1d(string $data, int $pos): int
671    {

675    /**
676     * Read 16-bit unsigned integer.
677     */
678    public static function getInt2d(string $data, int $pos): int
679    {
680        return ord($data[$pos]) | (ord($data[$pos + 1]) << 8);
681    }

683    /**
684     * Read 32-bit signed integer.
685     */
686    public static function getInt4d(string $data, int $pos): int
687    {
688        // FIX: represent numbers correctly on 64-bit system
689        // http://sourceforge.net/tracker/index.php?func=detail&aid=1487372&group_id=99160&atid=623334
690        // Hacked by Andreas Rehm 2006 to ensure correct result of the <<24 block on 32 and 64bit systems
691        $or24 = ord($data[$pos + 3]);
692
693        $ord24 = ($or24 & 127) << 24;
694        if ($or24 >= 128) {
695            // negative number
696            $ord24 = -abs((256 - $or24) << 24);
697        }
698
699        return ord($data[$pos]) | (ord($data[$pos + 1]) << 8) | (ord($data[$pos + 2]) << 16) | $ord24;
700    }
